HEADWORD: Forceless
<hw>Force"less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having little or no force;
feeble.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>These <qex>forceless</qex> flowers like sturdy trees support
me.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>forcefulness</ent>⟦br⟧
